data.description: Great location!!! Spacious home with spacious Bedrooms. Home has a lot nature light and includes close porch with air conditioner to enjoy in the hot summer weather. Efficient galley Kitchen with granite counters top and light kitchen cabinets. Residence with comfortable and spacious rooms.  Beautiful residence completely remodeled.  Roof replaced in 2019. Excellent location.  Surrounded by large shops and amusement parks.  Large and spacious laundry room to place warehouse shelf.  Additional room Ideal to enjoy with large windows and high clarity while having a pleasant temperature due to the residence's AC air conditioning. Owner it's open foe help with closing cost.
